      "span_text": "Oocytes were then washed by pipetting through five droplets of TALP supplemented with 5 mM HEPES and maintained up to 2 months in 0.5 M (NH 4 ) 2 SO 4, 0.75 M MgCl 2, 0.2 mM ZnCl 2 and 0.1 mg/ml of PVA, pH 7.4, at 48C, until use"
